graph TD
    A[Raw Data in S3] -->|Triggers| B[SageMaker Processing Job]
    B -->|Preprocessed Data| C[SageMaker Training Job]
    
    C -->|model.tar.gz| D[Evaluation Job]
    D -->|Accuracy Metrics| E{Accuracy > Threshold?}
    
    E -->|No| X[Pipeline Fails / Alert Data Scientist]
    E -->|Yes| F[Register in SageMaker Model Registry]
    
    subgraph Model Registry
    F --> G[Version 1.0: PendingManualApproval]
    G -.->|Lead Data Scientist Reviews| H[Version 1.0: Approved]
    end
    
    H -->|Triggers CI/CD| I[Deploy to Production Endpoint]
    
    J[Production Traffic] --> I
    I -.->|Monitors| K[Data / Concept Drift Detection]
    K -.->|Drift Detected| A
